27:48.242 --> 27:49.741
Thanks. Your big environment.

27:49.743 --> 27:52.310
- I'll let you guys clean up.
- Oh, sorry.

27:52.312 --> 27:54.178
What's up?

27:54.180 --> 27:56.747
