you know I'm taking over the...

27:56.749 --> 27:58.749
the yogurt ninja shop.

27:58.751 --> 28:00.951
Quicker.

28:00.953 --> 28:02.819
- Got that?
- I'm the quicker.

28:02.821 --> 28:05.321
You are quick on your heels.

28:05.323 --> 28:07.856
Um, and I wanted to apologize
for the barrage of e-mails

28:07.858 --> 28:09.757
that are headed your way.

28:09.759 --> 28:11.492
Yeah.

28:11.494 --> 28:14.828
So, I'm gonna send you one
with the latest details, then.

28:14.830 --> 28:17.463
- Okay.
- I hope your computer's okay.

28:17.465 --> 28:19.531
- I'll be fine, thanks.
- Nice to meet you, Ben.

28:19.533 --> 28:22.166
Good to meet you.

28:22.168 --> 28:24.067
See you, katelyn.

28:37.348 --> 28:39.948
[ Cows mooing ]

28:45.955 --> 28:48.555
Come here, tiger!

28:48.557 --> 28:51.024
Here, boy! Here, boy!

28:51.026 --> 28:53.860
Come here!

28:53.862 --> 28:55.695
You don't like me anymore.

28:55.697 --> 28:57.363
- Hey, there.
- Hello, dear.

28:57.365 --> 28:59.898
- How are you?
- Good, good.

28:59.900 --> 29:01.532
Uh-oh, look what you got?

29:01.534 --> 29:04.234
Oh, yeah, just got one
acting up in the basement.

29:04.236 --> 29:05.401
Coffee?

29:05.403 --> 29:07.836
- No, no, thanks.
- You sure?

29:07.838 --> 29:09.070
Yeah, yeah.

29:09.072 --> 29:11.705
I got to get going in a sec.

29:11.707 --> 29:13.707
Everything else been
going all right, though?

29:13.709 --> 29:15.875
Is Ben planning
on coming up real soon?

29:15.877 --> 29:19.011
Yeah, well, you know,
I don't know.

29:19.013 --> 29:20.412
