29:20.414 --> 29:23.081
I talked to him the other day.

29:23.083 --> 29:25.049
It seems like everything's
going real good.

29:25.051 --> 29:26.517
Great.

29:26.519 --> 29:28.552
Still does that computer stuff
down there?

29:28.554 --> 29:31.221
Yeah, he's doing
some commercials and stuff.

29:31.223 --> 29:33.389
I seen a couple
on TV the other day.

29:33.391 --> 29:35.057
Well, it sounds neat.

29:35.059 --> 29:37.592
Yeah, yeah, he's doing...

29:37.594 --> 29:40.561
doing okay in it.

29:40.563 --> 29:43.163
He's doing well.

29:43.165 --> 29:45.031
Oh.

29:45.033 --> 29:48.234
Say, how's your back?

29:48.236 --> 29:51.070
Dale said it looked like you got
cut up pretty good on something.

29:51.072 --> 29:54.239
