we'll do a duet or something.

01:02:22.654 --> 01:02:24.553
- Yeah, I could do it.
- Okay.

01:02:24.555 --> 01:02:26.588
Anyway, sorry that was kind
of a bust.

01:02:26.590 --> 01:02:28.656
