01:02:36.264 --> 01:02:37.896
No, I know, I know.

01:02:37.898 --> 01:02:40.698
No, I... I'm sorry.
No, I'm sorry.

01:02:40.700 --> 01:02:42.366
You know what?
I can't 'cause...

01:02:42.368 --> 01:02:44.501
it's okay,
I didn't have dinner,

01:02:44.503 --> 01:02:48.238
